query:
SELECT se.subjectId, se.professorId, 
       CASE WHEN EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM subjects s WHERE s.id = se.subjectId) THEN 'YES' ELSE 'NO' END as subject_exists
FROM student_enrollments se 
WHERE se.studentId = 1
LIMIT 10;
